ASI Token Migration

  • Phase 1: Rebranding & Merging Tokens - July 1st, 2024
    • Project Rebrand: Project name and logos change to Artificial Superintelligence Alliance (ASI).
    • Token Merge: AGIX and OCEAN tokens temporarily merge into FET on the Ethereum blockchain. (Holders on other chains need to bridge to Ethereum)
    • FET Trading: FET trading continues as usual. (Price reflects combined value of AGIX, OCEAN & FET)
    • Centralized Exchanges (CEX): No action is required. Automatic conversion of AGIX & OCEAN to FET on exchanges.
    • Self-Custody Wallets: Migrate AGIX & OCEAN to FET here.
    • Exchange Delisting: AGIX & OCEAN tokens begin delisting from exchanges.
  • Phase 2: ASI Deployment & Network Upgrade
    • FET to ASI: Token ticker updated to ASI
    • ASI Token Deployment: ASI token launches across multiple blockchains.
    • Network Upgrade: Fetch.ai network upgrades to the ASI network.
    • Migration Contracts: New contracts introduced to convert FET, AGIX, and OCEAN to ASI.
    • EVM & Bridges: Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) and other bridges open for ASI transfers.
    • Exchange Migration: Exchanges migrate spot markets from FET to ASI.
